channel.title: Wth is wrong!?!?!
channel.description: Ok, so everytime I go to get on Moparscape or the Silab Client it laggs like hell... It doesn't matter what server it is or which client, it always laggs.. And when I say lagg I mean it really laggs bad, I click somewhere and 2 minutes later my character will move... I really don't understand why. I mean I have a Dell XPS 400, Broadband Internet Connection (256Kbs), like 30G of memory left, so I don't understand why it laggs... Somebody please tell me if these computer specs are good enough or tell me how I can check stuff like that... thanks
